{"word":"G159 - αἴτιος - aítios - ah'-ee-tee-os - Author","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἴτιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aítios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ah'-ee-tee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Author</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"காரணர் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"the author, that in which the cause of anything resides, causative, causing"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G154 - αἰτέω - aitéō - ahee-teh'-o/154\">G154</a>; <i>causative</i>, that is, (concretely) a <i>causer:</i> - author.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}